{"tid":39143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家幾時開始對老友記失去憐憫之心？","createTime":"2016-12-14T11:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T12:40:59.000Z","uid":31979,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25371c6241d18db82217067f2ce93582dc9bddff","tid":39143,"uid":31979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"1. 以前見到老人家一定讓坐，而家返工放工見到梅下梅下就想屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 成日話鳩80/90後係廢青，自己當年點樣點樣認屎認屁<br />\n<br />\n3. 收完蛇齋餅糉就賣港投建制<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他原因？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正所謂百行以孝為先。華人社會受儒家思想影響甚廣，敬老可謂華人其中一種根深蒂固嘅價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n點解而家咁多後生會仇老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b9f0090f105c1fa138169a73399ccc743c3a27","tid":39143,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"為老不尊"},{"pid":"88b13c8185017ca87b10af44adf78c93aa9976aa","tid":39143,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"由佢地既態度極差開始<br />\n<br />\n會選擇性讓座，香港都有唔少好好既老友記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0e4ca9a97cec0d26bb50117f03058dc4622c65","tid":39143,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"2014開始"},{"pid":"c57bcd98ecc94bcbe30fa59923c0d303639e52a6","tid":39143,"uid":15063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"長而無述，老而不死是為賊也"},{"pid":"77f53df3c1ade4df1fa04786c5e1521553b7679c","tid":39143,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:44:46.000Z","m